<div class="content">
  <h3 class="subtitle">
    Installation
  </h3>

  {{#themed-syntax transparent="true" language="bash"}}
ember install ember-bulma
  {{/themed-syntax}}

  <br>
  <p>Then create a {{#bulma-tag}}ember-cli-sass{{/bulma-tag}} NPM dependency and create a SCSS file in your App called {{#bulma-tag}}styles/app.scss{{/bulma-tag}} with the following import statement:</p>

  {{#themed-syntax transparent="true" language="scss"}}
@import "bulma";
  {{/themed-syntax}}

  <h1 class="title is-5">Optional Addon</h1>
  {{#themed-syntax transparent="true" language="bash"}}
ember install ember-font-awesome
  {{/themed-syntax}}

  <h1 class="title is-5">Experimental</h1>

  <p><strong>Tree Shaking</strong> - exclude specified components from your build tree</p>
  {{#themed-syntax transparent="true" language="javascript"}}
// environment.js
var ENV = {
  // ...
  'ember-bulma': {
    except: ['bulma-tag'] // excludes `bulma-tag`
  }
}
  {{/themed-syntax}}


